## 5. Hardware & Receipt Printing (`esc_pos_utils_plus` & `flutter_blue_plus`)
Receipt generation is optimized for BLE-enabled mobile thermal ESC/POS roll printers.
* **Paper Formatting Configurations**: Supports three standard roll widths (defined in `lib/constants/enums.dart`):
  * **Small (mm58)**: 32 columns
  * **Medium (mm72)**: 42 columns
  * **Large (mm80)**: 48 columns
* **Dynamic Voucher Widget**: `lib/widgets/voucher_box_widget.dart` generates a high-quality visual receipt layout. This visual model is mirrored when converting layouts into binary printer-friendly byte-arrays.

